r message and the associated SQLCODE value.  </p> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-function.db2-stmt-error-parameters">  <h3 class="title">参数</h3>  <span>   <dl>         <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">stmt</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       A valid statement resource.      </p>     </dd>       </dl>  </span> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.db2-stmt-error-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   Returns a string containing an SQLSTATE value.  </p> </div>  <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.db2-stmt-error-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <span>   <ul class="simplelist">    <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link db2_conn_error()} - Returns a string containing the SQLSTATE returned by the last connection attempt</span></li>    <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link db2_conn_errormsg()} - Returns the last connection error message and SQLCODE value</span></li>    <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link db2_stmt_errormsg()} - Returns a string containing the last SQL statement error message</span></li>   </ul>  </span> </div></div>
